title: #68: Colored People (Al Jackson)
itunes:title: Colored People with Al Jackson - Part 1
description: Al Jackson stopped by Casa de Shaffir while he was in LA for a nice long talk about black people. Of course, I forgot to ask some key questions, but there was still plenty of time to have 3 hours of conversation about it. In case you didn't know, Al Jackson is black.
